# sap-snow
API for integration with ServiceNow

# JSON example for API call from ServiceNow
```json
{
  "ext_id": "CHG108823",  // change document in ServiceNow
  "sm_id": "",            // change document in SAP Solution Manager
  "description": "change in FI master data",
  "text": "Please adjust account master data according to description in attachment",
  "attachment": "",
  "filename": "corrections.pdf",
  "mimetype": "application/pdf"
}
```
